[30;1m20 | [0m[35mclass Ellipse(Conic):[0m
[30;1m21 | [0m[35m    """An ellipse is a curve defined by a coordinate system and a major and minor axis.[0m
[30;1m22 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m23 | [0m[35m    The centre of the ellipse is at the origin of the coordinate system.[0m
[30;1m24 | [0m[35m    The major axis is parallel to the local x-axis.[0m
[30;1m25 | [0m[35m    The minor axis is parallel to the local y-axis.[0m
[30;1m26 | [0m[35m    The parameter domain of an ellipse is ``[0, 2*pi]``.[0m
